			<h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4"> 
								What is DMCA?
							</h1>

			
						
			<div class="content_desc  no_follow_content  space-y-3 pb-5 pr-5">
				<p>If someone is stealing the content of your website and uploading it on your website, then you can complain about it. Through DMCA, you can keep your content safe and warn that person, if he still does not agree, then you can also take action on him.</p><p>This act was made in America by Bill Clinton. This act is applicable everywhere. Under this act, those people are punished who steal content from any website and upload it to their website.</p><h2>What is the benefit of the DMCA protected website?</h2><p>If you use DMCA Protection for your website, then you get some benefits which are mentioned below.</p><p>1. Using this increases the security of your blog.</p><p>2. By using DMCA Protection in your blog, if someone is stealing your content, then you can complain against him.<br></p><p>3. When you apply for this, you get a DMCA Protection Certificate. With this, if someone copies your content, then you can alert him by sending an alert message.<br></p><p>4. By adding DMCA, you can also get watermark in the image for free.<br></p><p>5. If you add DMCA then your blog is a Professional Show.<br></p>
			</div>
			
