                <div class="comment_desc mt-3 md:ml-0 -ml-16">
                    Full form of DMCA is Digital Millennium Copyright Act . This Act is a 1998 United States copyright law that implements two 1996 treaties of the World Intellectual Property Organization. It criminalizes production and dissemination of technology, devices, or services intended to circumvent measures that control access to copyrighted works.<br />

                </div>

